Installation Instructions
=========================
0/ Install gems listed in doc/REQUIREMENTS

1/ create a new rails applications:

rails my_new_app

2/ Add required plugins:

script/plugin install http://dev.rubyonrails.org/svn/plugins/exception_notification/
script/plugin install http://opensvn.csie.org/rails_file_column/plugins/file_column/trunk
script/plugin install http://svn.rails-engines.org/plugins/engines
script/plugin install http://svn.techno-weenie.net/projects/plugins/attachment_fu/
script/plugin install svn://projects.jkraemer.net/acts_as_ferret/tags/stable/acts_as_ferret

3/ Add bagel plugin
script/plugin install http://debian.dotproject.be/svn/bagel/trunk


#- evironment.rb
#- config/environments
#- application.rb
#- routes
#- remove index.html
#- copy schema.rb ?

rake db:schema:load
rake bagel:db:load

